

You create a unit /etc/systemd/system/mydaemon.service.

[Unit]
Description=MQ Adapter
After=syslog.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/xborder/message-adapter/bin/message-adapter
Restart=on-failure
StandardOutput=null

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target



systemctl start message-adapter

systemctl enable message-adapter




https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/reference/html/deployment.html

https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/426862/proper-way-to-run-shell-script-as-a-daemon
